item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Chivalrous Amoekens - Fanatic Voyage (FLAC)
item.description: Hey everyone, I'm looking for an album called Fanatic Voyage by Chivalrous Amoekens, a supergroup formed by Angel Olsen and Bonnie Prince Billy. I'm a big fan of Angel's and just found out about this album; I'd very much like to add it to my digital collection. If anyone is able to find it and is willing to share it, that would be amazing. Thanks in advance!
